- Licensed Commercial Banks (LCBs) must submit an application (BSD-MBU-01) to the Director of Bank Supervision (DBS) on a quarterly basis, 15 working days prior to the commencement of such quarter.
- The application should be submitted with a cover letter signed by the Chief Executive Officer/Chief Operating Officer or Deputy Chief Executive Officer.

